{"word":"Λευί","slug":"Λευί","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>Λευί, ὁ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Heb.\">Heb.</a>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ etym.\">etym.</a> unclear] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ indecl.\">indecl.</a> and <b><el>Λευίς</el>,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b><el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:Λευί\">Λευί</a></el>,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ acc.\">acc.</a> <b><el>Λευίν</el></b> <b>Levi<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> son of Jacob <b><a href='B:650 7:5'>Hb 7:5</a>, <a href='B:650 7:9'>9</a>; <a href='B:730 7:7'>Rv 7:7</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> son of Simeon and ancestor of Jesus <b><a href='B:490 3:29'>Lk 3:29</a>. <p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp></b> son of Melchi and ancestor of Jesus <b><a href='B:490 3:24'>Lk 3:24</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>4.</pp></b> a tax collector <b><a href='B:490 5:27'>Lk 5:27</a>, <a href='B:490 5:29'>29</a>;</b> as son of Alphaeus <b><a href='B:480 2:14'>Mk 2:14</a>.</b> On <b><a href='B:470 9:9'>Mt 9:9</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ s.\">s.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:Μαθθαῖος\">Μαθθαῖος</a></el>. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:λεπτός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:Λευίτης\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}